  <entry>
    <title>记录工作中的开发规范</title>
    <link href="/2021/09/01/%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83/"/>
    <url>/2021/09/01/%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>记录在工作中提到的<strong>开发规范</strong>：</p><ul><li>在负责项目接口实现与前端进行对接的时候，出现了很多bug，改了好几天也长了记性</li><li>在对接的过程中还有别人的建议，是时候记录一下，规范自己以后的开发模式</li></ul><h1 id="正片开始"><a href="#正片开始" class="headerlink" title="正片开始"></a>正片开始</h1><h2 id="接口返回统一数据格式"><a href="#接口返回统一数据格式" class="headerlink" title="接口返回统一数据格式"></a>接口返回统一数据格式</h2><blockquote><p>现在是前后端分离的时代，在编写后端开发时要返回统一数据格式(一般都是json字符串)，这样才能更好的查看返回的结果</p></blockquote><p>一般包含：</p><ul><li>信息 Message</li><li>状态码 Code</li><li>结果 Result/Data</li><li>时间戳 Timestamp</li></ul><div class="note note-info">            <p>代码示例 </p>          </div><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Result</span>&lt;<span class="hljs-title">T</span>&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">implements</span> <span class="hljs-title">Serializable</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">final</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">long</span> serialVersionUID = <span class="hljs-number">1L</span>;<br>    <br>     <span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * 返回处理消息</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     */</span><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@ApiModelProperty(value = &quot;返回处理消息&quot;)</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> String message = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;操作成功！&quot;</span>;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * 返回代码</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     */</span><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@ApiModelProperty(value = &quot;返回代码&quot;)</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> Integer code = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * 返回数据对象 data</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     */</span><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@ApiModelProperty(value = &quot;返回数据对象&quot;)</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> T result;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * 时间戳</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     */</span><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@ApiModelProperty(value = &quot;时间戳&quot;)</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">long</span> timestamp = System.currentTimeMillis();<br>    <br>     <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> &lt;T&gt; <span class="hljs-function">Result&lt;T&gt; <span class="hljs-title">OK</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>        Result&lt;T&gt; r = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> Result&lt;T&gt;();<br>        r.setSuccess(<span class="hljs-keyword">true</span>);<br>        r.setCode(CommonConstant.SC_OK_200);<br>        r.setMessage(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;成功&quot;</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> r;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> &lt;T&gt; <span class="hljs-function">Result&lt;T&gt; <span class="hljs-title">OK</span><span class="hljs-params">(T data)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        Result&lt;T&gt; r = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> Result&lt;T&gt;();<br>        r.setSuccess(<span class="hljs-keyword">true</span>);<br>        r.setCode(CommonConstant.SC_OK_200);<br>        r.setResult(data);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> r;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> &lt;T&gt; <span class="hljs-function">Result&lt;T&gt; <span class="hljs-title">OK</span><span class="hljs-params">(String msg, T data)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        Result&lt;T&gt; r = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> Result&lt;T&gt;();<br>        r.setSuccess(<span class="hljs-keyword">true</span>);<br>        r.setCode(CommonConstant.SC_OK_200);<br>        r.setMessage(msg);<br>        r.setResult(data);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> r;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> Result&lt;Object&gt; <span class="hljs-title">error</span><span class="hljs-params">(String msg)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> error(CommonConstant.SC_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR_500, msg);<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> Result&lt;Object&gt; <span class="hljs-title">error</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> code, String msg)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        Result&lt;Object&gt; r = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> Result&lt;Object&gt;();<br>        r.setCode(code);<br>        r.setMessage(msg);<br>        r.setSuccess(<span class="hljs-keyword">false</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> r;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> Result&lt;T&gt; <span class="hljs-title">error500</span><span class="hljs-params">(String message)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.message = message;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.code = CommonConstant.SC_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR_500;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.success = <span class="hljs-keyword">false</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note note-danget">            <p>其中的常量需要自行定义 eg：<code>public static final Integer SC_OK_200 = 200;</code></p>          </div><p><img src="/2021/09/01/%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83/image-20210901173505326.png" alt="返回结果"></p><p>我之前在学校写的项目简直没有规范可言 $%^&amp;*^##@!# 最近在准备毕设和负责项目才接触到 TAT</p><h2 id="查询提供自定义排序"><a href="#查询提供自定义排序" class="headerlink" title="查询提供自定义排序"></a>查询提供自定义排序</h2><p>案发现场：</p><p><img src="/2021/09/01/%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83/image-20210901174317864.png" alt="不忍直视"></p><p>​             **因为项目是集成了Jeecg boot所以我认为他有默认的排序/// ^ /// 而且不能修改SQL语句 **</p><p>实现后进一步建议：</p><p><img src="/2021/09/01/%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83/image-20210901173947766.png" alt="建议"></p><blockquote><p>一般分页查询都有两个固定的参数</p><ul><li>pageSize 页面大小</li><li>pageNo 当前页数</li></ul></blockquote><p>现在就多加一个字段<code>orderby</code>来控制排序的顺序和要排序的字段</p><div class="note note-info">            <p>代码示例</p>          </div><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> Result&lt;?&gt; list(OpendayLive opendayLive,<br>                                   <span class="hljs-meta">@RequestParam(name = &quot;pageNo&quot;, defaultValue = &quot;1&quot;)</span> Integer pageNo,<br>                                   <span class="hljs-meta">@RequestParam(name = &quot;pageSize&quot;, defaultValue = &quot;10&quot;)</span> Integer pageSize,<br>                                   <span class="hljs-meta">@RequestParam(name = &quot;orderby&quot;,defaultValue = &quot;&quot;)</span> String orderby,<br>                                   HttpServletRequest req) &#123;<br>        QueryWrapper&lt;OpendayLive&gt; queryWrapper = QueryGenerator.initQueryWrapper(opendayLive, req.getParameterMap());<br>        Page&lt;OpendayLive&gt; page = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> Page&lt;OpendayLive&gt;(pageNo, pageSize);<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">//判断orderby是否为空</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!StrUtil.isBlank(orderby))&#123;<br>            String[] orderBy = orderby.split(<span class="hljs-string">&quot; &quot;</span>);<br>            String param = orderBy[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>];<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-string">&quot;asc&quot;</span>.equals(param) || <span class="hljs-string">&quot;ASC&quot;</span>.equals(param))&#123;<br>                queryWrapper.orderByAsc(orderBy[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]);<br>            &#125;<span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123;<br>                queryWrapper.orderByDesc(orderBy[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]);<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>        IPage&lt;OpendayLive&gt; pageList = opendayLiveService.page(page, queryWrapper);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> Result.OK(pageList);<br>    &#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>个人感觉怪怪的，有好想法可以告诉我。。。但可以基本实现自定义排序了！！</p><h2 id="返回正确的状态码"><a href="#返回正确的状态码" class="headerlink" title="返回正确的状态码"></a>返回正确的状态码</h2><p>又一案发现场：</p><p><img src="/2021/09/01/%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83/image-20210901180048905.png" alt="建议建议"></p><p>这是我还没搞懂返回统一的数据结构时埋下的坑，，破案了 填坑了</p><p><strong>500是表示服务器错误！！没有查找数据是正确执行了方法，只是空</strong></p><p><img src="/2021/09/01/%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83/image-20210901180208016.png" alt="埋坑现场"></p><p>导致前端按照500去判断了。。。</p><div class="note note-info">            <p>填坑</p>          </div><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> Result&lt;?&gt; get() &#123;<br>        QueryWrapper&lt;OpendayLiveNotice&gt; wrapper = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> QueryWrapper&lt;&gt;();<br>        OpendayLiveNotice opendayLiveNotice = opendayLiveNoticeService.getOne(wrapper);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (opendayLiveNotice == <span class="hljs-keyword">null</span>) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> Result.ok(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;未找到对应数据&quot;</span>);<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> Result.OK(opendayLiveNotice);<br>    &#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>实习还在继续，，，</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
